  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Coherent parametric X-radiation by the train of charged particles bunches: Conditions of observation</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="260" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="c">2017-03-19</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">The problem of coherent parametric X-radiation (PXR) by the electron bunch is considered. The PXR by different electrons could be coherent at small bunch dimensions. Conditions for this kind of radiation – coherent PXR (CPXR) – were considered. Features of CPXR by the bunch as well as by the train of bunches are demonstrated.</subfield>
